<paragraph blockId="6.[151,1436,869,1254]" pageId="6" pageNumber="543">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,352,1193,1218]" pageId="6" pageNumber="543">Distribution.</emphasis>
Europe including Southern half of European 
<collectingCountry box="[878,955,1193,1218]" name="Russia" pageId="6" pageNumber="543">Russia</collectingCountry>
